column2:
for (r in 1:nrow(psub)){
    #Entry Subset
    e<-psub[r,]
    
    #Subset Vectors
    desc<-e$Description
    photo<-paste("![",desc,"](portfolio/",e$Filename,".jpg){height: 200px;} ",sep="")
    
    cat("::: {}","\n","\n")
    cat(photo,"\n","\n","\n")
    cat(":::","\n","\n")
  }
![Two horses in a stall with heads over fence](portfolio/Animals_LazyDay.jpg){height: 200px;}
